OL,3,CHear from the candidates for Tees
OL,4,CValley Mayor
OL,6,FThere are three candidates standing in
OL,7,Fthe third election for Tees Valley
OL,8,FMayor, on Thursday 2 May.
OL,10,FThe winner will lead the combined
OL,11,Fauthority, which brings together
OL,12,FDarlington, Hartlepool, Middlesbrough,
OL,13,FRedcar & Cleveland and Stockton.
OL,15,FThey will have control of significant
OL,16,Ffunding and powers over things like
OL,17,Ftransport, regeneration and skills.
OL,19,FWe have spoken to the candidates to
OL,20,Fhear their pledges.
