OL,3,CHear from the candidates for Tees
OL,4,CValley Mayor
OL,6,FConservative Ben Houchen has been the
OL,7,Fmayor since 2017, and is hoping for a
OL,8,Fthird term.
OL,10,FHe was made a member of the House of
OL,11,FLords last year.He says North Tees
OL,12,FHospital is "falling down" and he
OL,13,Fplans to build a replacement, as well
OL,14,Fas providing free swimming for
OL,15,Fchildren under 11, and introducing
OL,16,Fmore flights from Teesside Airport "to
OL,17,Fplaces like Malaga and Tenerife."
