OL,3,CHear from the candidates for Tees
OL,4,CValley Mayor
OL,6,FLabour candidate Chris McEwan is the
OL,7,Fdeputy leader of Darlington Borough
OL,8,FCouncil, and a former NHS manager.
OL,10,FHe said his priorities were growing
OL,11,Fthe economy, "turbo-charging the
OL,12,Fskills system", creating "an
OL,13,Fintegrated transport system", and
OL,14,Fproviding free parking in town centres.
OL,16,FMr McEwan told us he would be able to
OL,17,Fput the Tees Valley on the map, due to
OL,18,Fhis "regional connections and national
OL,19,Fconnections."
